==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exsect
<hw>Ex*sect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exsectio</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A cutting out or
away.</def> <rj><au>E. Darwin.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Surg.)</fld> <def>The removal by operation of a
portion of a limb; particularly, the removal of a portion of a bone in
the vicinity of a joint; the act or process of cutting out.</def></p>

